  HTS_AP_Bridge_Defs.h  (M4↔A55 앱 계약; 핸드셰이크: IPC AP_CONTRACT_REQ/RSP 0x42/0x43)
  HTS_Network_Bridge.h → .cpp
  HTS_KT_DSN_Adapter.h → .cpp
